0M Continue normal activities but be watchful for suspicious activities.
Report criminal activity to local law enforcement.
0M Review family emergency plans.
0M Increase family emergency preparedness by purchasing supplies, food and storing water.
0M Be familiar with local natural and technological (man made) hazards in your community.
0M Increase individual or family emergency preparedness through training, maintaining good physical fitness and health, and storing food, water and emergency supplies.
0M Monitor local and national news for terrorist alerts.
0M Update immunizations and maintain records.
0M Volunteer to assist and support the community emergency response agencies.
